      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-4 mb-6">How to Convert Your Salla Store Into a Native Mobile App</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-8">Boost conversions, LTV and brand presence by converting your Salla store into a mobile app. Tap into the mobile market and provide a seamless shopping experience for your loyal customers.</p>
    </div>
